er%2C%20to%20help%20ensure%20faster%20recovery%20for%20their%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20a%20village%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Dr%20Sumitra%20was%20no%20stranger%20to%20the%20problems%20people%20in%20remote%20areas%20face%20in%20accessing%20healthcare.%20To%20address%20these%20challenges%20and%20provide%20instant%20care%20for%20children%2C%20she%20started%20Babynama%2C%20a%20digital%20paediatric%20care%20platform%2C%20in%202022.%20Her%20husband%2C%20Ashish%20Meena%2C%20an%20IIT%20Bombay%20graduate%20with%20over%20a%20decade%20of%20experience%20in%20startups%2C%20joined%20the%20company%20a%20few%20months%20later%20as%20co-founder%2C%20quitting%20his%20job%20to%20support%20the%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20they%20have%20helped%20nearly%20two%20lakh%20parents%20access%20timely%20care%20and%20identify%20early%20signs%20of%20critical%20conditions%20such%20as%20respiratory%20distress%2C%20epilepsy%2C%20autism%2C%20and%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EADHD%20in%20children%2C%20ensuring%20timely%20medical%20intervention%20and%20better%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProviding%20baby%20healthcare%20round%20the%20clock%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Dausa%20district%2C%20Dr%20Sumitra%2C%2035%2C%20had%20experienced%20tragedy%20in%20her%20own%20family%20as%20a%20child.%20Her%20sister%20had%20passed%20away%20just%20hours%20after%20birth%20as%20she%20was%20delivered%20at%20home%2C%20and%20they%20lacked%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F369628%2Fendometriosis-gynaecologists-womens-health-pain-periods-menstrual-cramps-devleena-chatterjee-sneha-khedkar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccess%20to%20immediate%20healthcare.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20personal%20loss%20motivated%20Dr%20Sumitra%2C%20then%20a%20young%20girl%2C%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20medicine.%20As%20th