ing-cant-catch-ukraine-air-force-top-us-general-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edispersal%20tactics%20Ukraine%20has%20been%20employing%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20keep%20Russians%20from%20destroying%20its%20smaller%20air%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jet's%20flexibility%20makes%20it%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20better%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20a%20country%20that's%20bordering%20an%20aggressor%2C%26quot%3B%20Bohnert%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou'll%20probably%20get%20more%20effectiveness%20out%20of%20an%20F-16%20against%20Russia%20out%20of%20Germany%2C%20whereas%20the%20Gripen%20will%20get%20more%20capability%20out%20of%20Ukraine%20or%20some%20other%20bordering%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gripen%20is%20also%20a%20lighter%20maintenance%20lift%20than%20some%20other%20aircraft%2C%20the%20F-16%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20F-16%20fighter%20jet%20flying%20across%20gray%20skies.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cdcf3d1aa2ac29ee348231%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221933%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Ukrainian%20air%20force%20F-16%20fighter%20jet%20flies%20in%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20in%20Ukraine%20on%20August%204.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FEfrem%20Lukatsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20at%20the%20UK-based%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rusi.org%2FSR-Russian-Air-War-Ukraine-web-final.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%20that%20of%20available%20Western%20aircraft%20that%20could%20be%20supplied%2C%20the%20Gripen%20%26quot%3Boffers%20by%20far%20the%20most%20suitable%20candidate%20in%20terms%20of%20operational%20requirements.%20It%20was%20designed%20from%20the%20outset%20for%20ease%20of%20maintenance%2C%20and%20can%20be%20refuelled%2C%20re-armed%20and%20given%20basic%20maintenance%20by%20teams%20of%20just%20six