ment%20for%20a%20post-conflict.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gripen%20could%20be%20a%20good%20alternative%20if%20US%20support%20suddenly%20collapsed%2C%20but%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%20Ukraine%20has%20its%20hands%20full%20building%20an%20F-16%20fleet%20and%20the%20approaching%20task%20of%20integrating%20Mirages%20into%20its%20air%20force%2C%20which%20Sweden%20has%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Ukraine's%20long-term%20defense%20needs%20will%20almost%20certainly%20center%20on%20Russia%2C%20which%20will%20be%20a%20threat%20to%20Ukraine%20no%20matter%20how%20this%20war%20ends.%20That%20makes%20the%20Swedish%20Gripen%20a%20worthwhile%20consideration%20for%20its%20long-term%20fighter%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Swedish%20Saab%20JAS%2039%20Gripen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F633c4a754d423e0018203b86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221095%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESaab%20JAS%2039%20Gripens%20taxi.%3Cp%3EPATRICK%20TRAGARDH%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aa367036-bb90-4206-9e70-24b66258ea1e%5C%22%3EUkraine's%20future%20air%20force%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAir%20warfare%20experts%20have%20described%20Ukraine's%20acquisition%20of%20its%20first%20F-16s%20as%20the%20beginning%20of%20building%20Ukraine's%20long-term%20air%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20officials%20have%20also%20described%20it%20as%20a%20long-term%20project%2C%20with%20Defense%20Secretary%20Lloyd%20Austin%20saying%20last%20year%20that%20the%20US%20would%20lead%20a%20coalition%20focused%20on%20increasing%20the%20Ukrainian%20air%20force's%20ability%20to%20defend%20itself%20against%20Russia%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gripen%20is%20good%2C%20but%20the%20F-16%20is%20probably%20the%20best%20option%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyi%20in%20front