20Sidhu%20Moosewala%20in%202022%2C%20the%20firing%20outside%20actor%20Salman%20Khan's%20residence%20in%20Bandra%20in%20April%20and%20the%20killing%20of%20politician%20Baba%20Siddique%20earlier%20this%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChargesheets%20were%20filed%20against%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%2C%20who%20is%20from%20Fazilka%20in%20Punjab%2C%20in%20two%20cases%20registered%20by%20the%20NIA%20in%202022%20and%20he%20fled%20India%20on%20a%20fake%20passport%20last%20year.%20He%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20in%20Canada.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnmol%20has%20at%20least%2018%20cases%20against%20him%20and%20allegedly%20provided%20weapons%20and%20logistical%20support%20to%20the%20men%20who%20gunned%20down%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%20near%20his%20village%20Moosa%20in%20Punjab's%20Mansa%20district%20on%20June%2029%2C%202022.%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20member%20Goldy%20Brar%20had%20taken%20responsibility%20for%20the%20killing%20and%20later%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20carried%20out%20to%20avenge%20the%20murder%20of%20Vicky%20Muddukhera%2C%20a%20Youth%20Akali%20Dal%20leader.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20responsibility%20for%20the%20firing%20outside%20Salman%20Khan's%20residence%2C%20Galaxy%20Apartments%20in%20Bandra%2C%20was%20claimed%20by%20Anmol%20Bishnoi.%20A%20chargesheet%20filed%20in%20the%20case%20said%20that%20before%20the%20firing%20on%20April%2014%2C%20Bishnoi%20delivered%20a%20nine-minute%20speech%20to%20motivate%20the%20shooters%2C%20Vicky%20Gupta%20and%20Sagar%20Pal%2C%20telling%20them%20that%20they%20were%20on%20course%20to%20create%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLord%20Ram%20has%20blessed%20us.%20We%20will%20handle%20him%20(Salman%20Khan).%20There%20is%20no%20problem%2C%20as%20long%20as%20it%20is%20in%20my%20control%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20shooters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20it%20is%20do%20or%20die%2C%20either%20life%20or%20death.%20It%20is%20written%20by%20God.%20Either%20the%20bullets%20will%20be%20fired%20in%20the%20morning%20or%20we%20will%20sit%20at%20home.%20It%20is%20in%20your%20hands%20what%20to%20do%20and%20what%20not%20to%20do..%2C%20%C2%A0If%20you%20work%2C%20then%20history%20will%20be%20created.%20You%20will%20fill%20the%20newspapers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chargesheet%20had%20said%20the%20plan%20had%20been%20conceived%20in%20August%20last%20year%20and%20finetuned%20until%20it%20was%20finally%20carried%20out%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20a%20court%20in%20Mumbai%20had%20issued%20a%20non-bailable%20warrant%20against%20Anmol%20Bishnoi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Maharashtra%20minister%20and%20three-time%20MLA%20Baba%20Siddique%20was%20shot%20dead%20on%20Dussehra%20on%20October%2012%20outside%20the%20office%20of%20his%20son%20and%20MLA%20Zeeshan%20Siddique.%20Officials%20have%20said%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20shooters%20in%20this%20case%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20shooters%2C%20Gurmail%20Baljit%20Singh%20from%20Haryana%20and%20Dharamraj%20Kashyap%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20were%20arrested%20soon%20after%20the%20killing%20while%20Shiv%20Kumar%20Gautam%2C%20who%20is%20also%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20is%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729856040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F2h66kqpo_anmol_625x300_25_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsalman-khan-baba-siddique-sidhu-moosewala-who-is-anmol-bishnoi-lawrence-bishnois-brother-and-accused-in-key-cases-6871583%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lawrence%20Bishnoi's%20younger%20brother%20Anmol%20has%20shot%20into%20the%20spotlight%20after%20he%20was%20added%20to%20the%20most-wanted%20list%20of%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20and%20a%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20reward%20was%20announced%20for%20his%20arrest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndt