%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspirit-airlines-ticket-changes-bundled-fares-bags-snacks-premium-seats-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpirit%20announced%20new%20ticket%20bundles%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20appeal%20to%20higher-paying%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpirit%20also%20said%20Thursday%20it%20plans%20to%20implement%20%2480%20million%20of%20cost%20reductions%20early%20next%20year%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0primarily%20by%20cutting%20staff%20given%20the%20expected%20fall%20in%20flight%20volume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airline's%20stock%20rose%20around%2012%25%20in%20pre-market%20trading%20Friday%2C%20suggesting%20Spirit%20may%20have%20found%20a%20route%20to%20avoid%20bankruptcy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpirit%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20sent%20outside%20regular%20US%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspirit-airlines-unveils-cost-cutting-measures-amid-bankruptcy-reports-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729854434000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671b70bda0a0cc14f223d886%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspirit-airlines-unveils-cost-cutting-measures-amid-bankruptcy-reports-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Spirit%20Airlines%20has%20struggled%20since%20its%20proposed%20merger%20with%20JetBlue%20was%20struck%20down.%20Reports%20have%20emerged%20in%20recent%20weeks%20it%20is%20exploring%20bankruptcy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22psyme%40businessinsider.com%20(Pete%20Syme)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspirit-airlines-unveils-cost-cutting-measures-amid-bankruptcy-reports-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Superboys%20Of%20Malegaon%3A%20A%20Wake-Up%20Call%20For%20Bollywood%2C%20Which%20Loves%20Itself%20Too%20Much%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fu1span2_superboys_625x300_25_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20surface%2C%20Reema%20Kagti's%20latest%20feature%2C%20%3Cem%3ESuperboys%20of%20Malegaon%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2024)%2C%20is%20the%20story%20behind%20the%20story%20of%20a%20motley%20group%20of%20film%20enthusiasts%20from%20the%20eponymous%20city%2C%20who%20made%20low-budget%20parodies%20of%20famed%20Bollywood%20and%20Hollywood%20films.%20To%20subject%20Kagti's%20film%20to%20a%20surface-level%20reading%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20disservice%20to%20not%20just%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20intelligent%20storytellers%20but%20also%20to%20the%20industry%20which%2C%20with%20every%20passing%20film%2C%20dissolves%20into%20a%20decadent%20and%20dramatically%20stagnant%20being.%20A%20nation%20where%20any%20existence%20of%20artistic%20intelligence%20is%20strangled%20by%20moneymaking%20goons%20masquerading%20as%20film%20producers%2C%20who%20continue%20to%20push%20lacklustre%20universes%20of%20IP-driven%20dross%20where%20nothing%20that%20glitters%20is%20actually%20gold.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EWriter%20Baap%20Hota%20Hai%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKagti's%20film%2C%20albeit%20set%20in%20a%20place%20some%20270%20km%20and%2025%20years%20in%20the%20past%20from%20today's%20Bollywood%2C%20offers%20considerate%20commentary%2C%20for%20anyone%20willing%20to%20listen%2C%20on%20the%20times%20we%20live%20in.%20%E2%80%9CWriter%20baap%20hota%20hai%2C%E2%80%9D%20screams%20Farogh%20Jafri%20(Vineet%20Kumar%20Singh)%2C%20an%20underappreciated%20writer%20from%20Malegaon%2C%20when%20his%20original%20stories%20are%20repeatedly%20rejected%20by%20Nasir%20Shaikh%20(Adarsh%20Gourav)%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20their%20ragtag%20film%20crew%2C%20in%20favour%20of%20more%20parodies.%20While%20this%20dialogue%2C%20penned%20by%20Varun%20Grover%2C%20exists%20within%20the%20time-space%20continuum%20populated%20by%20this%20specific%20group%20from%20Malegaon%2C%20it%20evokes%20an%20emotion%20that%20transcends%20all%20borders%2C%20tangible%20or%20intangible.%20A%20similar%20emotion%20was%20evoked%20some%20400%20years%20ago%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98baap'%20of%20all%20writers%2C%20William%20Shakespeare%2C%20when%20he%20penned%20down%20his%20sonnet%2C%20%3Cem%3ENot%20Marble%20nor%20the%20Gilded%20Monuments%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20stating%20as%20fearlessly%20as%20Jafri%2C%20%E2%80%9CNot%20marble%20nor%20the%20gilded%20monuments%2C%20Of%20princes%20shall%20outlive%20this%20powerful%20rhyme.%E2%80%9D%20Nothing%20supersedes%20a%20good%20writer.%20And%20if%20Shakespeare%20and%20Grover%20said%20it%2C%20then%20it%20must%20be%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20quite%20remarkable%20then%20that%20this%20simple%20thought%20that%20has%20defied%20artistic%20evolution%20from%20its%20very%20inception%20remains%20incomprehensible%20for%20filmmakers%20and%20producers%20in%20India.%20Underpaid%20screenwriters%20underscore%20the%20reality%20of%20every%20film%20set%2C%20successful%20or%20unsuccessful%2C%20large%20or%20small.%20Ours%20is%20an%20industry%20that%20has%20not%20merely%20normalised%20this%20disparity%20but%20has%20also%20vigorously%20facilitated%20the%20culture%20of%20hero%20worship%2C%20which%20further%20curtails%20writers'%20wages%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20bigger%20paycheck%20for%20an%20actor%20who%20would%20be%20fundamentally%20unemployed%2C%20if%20not%20for%20the%20writer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENasir%20Understands%20A%20Complex%20Truth%20About%20Identity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parodies%20with%20an%20accentuated%20Malegaon%20accent%20in%20the%20film%20emphasise%20another%20important%20idea%20in%20this%20vein%E2%80%94the%20importance%20of%20socially%20and%20culturally%20cognisant%20writers%20and%20filmmakers.%20The%20granular%20motivation%20for%20these%20superboys%20of%20Malegaon%20was%20to%20create%20a%20cinema%20that%20cements%20their%20identity%20on%20the%20big%20screen%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20is%20not%20offered%20to%20people%20of%20their%20economic%20and%20social%20belonging%20by%20the%20system.%20It%20is%20but%20Bombay's%20cruelty%20that%20it%20teaches%20you%20to%20dream.%20Nevertheless%2C%20a%20replication%20of%20Bombay's%20glamourous%20filmmaking%20remains%20incredibly%20important%20as%20films%2C%20above%20all%20else%2C%20are%20entertainment%2C%20especially%20in%20Malegaon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20lost%20on%20Nasir%20that%20his%20films%20are%20meant%20to%20be%20seen%20by%20loom%20workers%20and%20farmhands%20who%20work%20too%20hard%20for%20too%20little%20in%20a%20place%20where%20nothing%20ever%20happens.%20To%20infuse%20Malegaon's%20desperation%20with%20the%20dynamism%20of%20Mumbai%20thus%20becomes%20his%20primary%20goal.%20What%20this%20requires%2C%20however%2C%20is%20an%20acute%20understanding%20of%20both%20lands%E2%80%94Malegaon%20and%20Mumbai.%20A%20familiarity%20with%20the%20texts%20and%20lives%20of%20both%20their%20source%20material%20and%20their%20reference%20material.%20A%20realisation%20that%20would%20save%20Bollywood%20bigwigs%20crores%20of%20rupees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESame%20Old%2C%20Same%20Old%20Bollywood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBollywood's%20is%20a%20rich%20history%20of%20self-referential%2C%20self-aware%20cinema.%20However%2C%20of%20late%2C%20there%20has%20been%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20need%20to%20refer%20sans%20innovation.%20An%20attitude%20that%20extends%20itself%20from%20major%20plot%20points%20to%20throwaway%20one-liners.%20We%20no%20longer%20have%20jokes%3B%20we%20have%20reminders%20of%20comedies%20released%20a%20decade%20ago.%20Humour%20manifests%20itself%20through%20arduous%20meta-textual%20and%20pop%20culture%20references%20as%20we%20laugh%20at%20feeble%20echoes%20of%20the%20same%20punchline%20perpetually%20reverberating%20across%20the%20hollow%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECutting%20decisively%20through%20the%20sparkling%20exterior%2C%20%3Cem%3ESuperboys%20%3C%2Fem%3Ealso%20magnifies%20the%20physical%2C%20emotional%2C%20and%20financial%20stresses%20that%20burden%20filmmakers.%20Observing%20the%20Malegaon%20filmmakers%20toil%20tirelessly%20amidst%20societal%20and%20economic%20restrictions%20to%20deliver%20films%20with%20heart%20and%20soul%20puts%20into%20perspective%20exactly%20how%20detrimental%20it%20is%20when%20Bollywood%20churns%20out%20movies%20worth%20hundreds%20of%20crores%20with%20no%20ambition.%20Filmmaking%20is%20a%20privilege%2C%20as%20professed%20by%20Kagti's%20picture%2C%20and%20it%20is%20evident%20that%20not%20just%20the%20filmmakers%20of%20Malegaon%20but%20the%20filmmakers%20in%20Malegaon%20recognised%20and%20responded%20to%20the%20duties%20that%20accompany%20this%20privilege.%20Unfortunately%2C%20this%20maturity%20eludes%20most%20of%20Bollywood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESuperboys%20%3C%2Fem%3EIs%20Filmmaking%20Free%20Of%20Constraint%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20film's%20ideas%20are%20eloquently%20expressed%20through%20Varun%20Grover's%20deliberate%20dialogues%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20that%20is%20to%20be%20understood%20from%20the%20film's%20silences%20as%20well.%20Faiza%20Ahmad%20Khan's%20%3Cem%3ESupermen%20of%20Malegaon%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2008)%2C%20the%20documentary%20film%20that%20in%20many%20ways%20inspired%20Kagti's%20fictional%20account%2C%20addressed%20the%20communal%20differences%20between%20Malegaon's%20population%20and%20how%20the%20build-up%20of%20a%20majority%20Muslim%20and%20a%20minority%20Hindu%20population%20impacts%20the%20access%20to%20and%20attitudes%20towards%20cinema.%20%3Cem%3ESuperboys%20of%20Malegaon%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20however%2C%20decides%20not%20to%20address%20this%20side%20of%20Malegaon's%20history%2C%20which%20doesn't%20come%20as%20much%20of%20a%20surprise%20in%20today's%20Bollywood%2C%20where%20extremist%20groups%20exercise%20undue%20but%20immense%20influence%20across%20the%20industry%3B%20one%20does%20understand%20the%20weight%20that%20this%20decision%20carries.%20The%20permanence%20of%20celluloid%20also%20means%20that%20this%20silence%20will%20ring%20loud%20forevermore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20core%2C%20however%2C%20%3Cem%3ESuperboys%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20story%20of%20liberated%20filmmaking.%20Free%20from%20all%20conventions%20of%20form%2C%20style%2C%20and%20substance%2C%20and%20in%20pursuit%20of%20euphoria.%20You%20feel%20it%20in%20the%20characters'%20motivations%2C%20and%20you%20read%20it%20on%20their%20faces.%20When%20they%20laugh%2C%20you%20laugh%20with%20them.%20When%20they%20cry%2C%20you%20shed%20a%20tear%20as%20well.%20It%20is%20honest%20filmmaking%20by%20a%20filmmaker%20who%20has%20remained%20demonstrably%20diligent%20towards%20her%20craft%2C%20about%20filmmakers%20who%20were%20nothing%20short%20of%20being%20dedicatedly%20determined%20towards%20theirs.%20And%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20%3Cem%3ESuperboys%20of%20Malegaon%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20joyous%20film%20that%20celebrates%20everyone%20who%20has%20ever%20made%20a%20film.%20It%20applauds%20all%20filmmakers%20who%20are%20unable%20to%20or%20unwilling%20to%20break%20through%20Bombay's%20hardened%20exterior.%20It%20is%20a%20film%20about%20everyone%20who%20is%20not%20a%20Bollywood%20bigwig%2C%20but%20quite%20poetically%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20must%20for%20everyone%20who%20is.%20A%20wake-up%20call%20for%20a%20fraternity%20that%20has%20only%20ever%20learnt%20to%20flatter%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nidhil%20Vohra%20is%20a%20writer%2C%20filmmaker%2C%20and%20film%20studies%20student%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Toronto.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729854300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%