uraging%20progress%20in%20various%20sectors%20of%20our%20strategic%20relations.%20There%20has%20been%20increasing%20cooperation%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20defence%2C%20technology%2C%20energy%2C%20green%20and%20sustainable%20development%20that%20have%20become%20symbols%20of%20mutual%20trust%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20also%20welcomed%20the%20'Focus%20on%20India'%20strategy%20announced%20by%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20delighted%20that%20to%20expand%20and%20elevate%20our%20partnership%2C%20we%20are%20taking%20several%20new%20and%20important%20initiatives%20and%20moving%20from%20the%20'Whole%20of%20Government'%20to%20the%20Whole%20of%20Nation%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IGC%20framework%20was%20launched%20in%202011%20and%20allows%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20review%20of%20cooperation%20and%20identification%20of%20new%20areas%20of%20engagement%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20across%20various%20sectors.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729850400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fm5vu5teo_narendra-modi-olaf-scholz-german-chancellor-pti_625x300_25_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findo-german-ties-strong-anchor-in-times-of-conflict-uncertainty-pm-narendra-modi-6870568%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20said%20the%20strategic%20partnership%20between%20India%20and%20Germany%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20strong%20anchor%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20world%20is%20faced%20with%20tensions%2C%20conflicts%20and%20uncertainty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findo-german-ties-strong-anchor-in-times-of-conflict-uncertainty-pm-narendra-modi-6870568%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jio%20Diwali%20Dhamaka%20offers%20free%20Swiggy%2C%20Ajio%20vouchers%20with%20these%20plans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729849868000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114581340%2Cimgsize-50676.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Freliance-jio-announces-diwali-dhamaka-offers-swiggy-ajio-and-easemytrip-vouchers-with-these-plans%2Farticleshow%2F114581384.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reliance%20Jio%20announces%20its%20True%205G%20Diwali%20Dhamaka%20offer%20with%20benefits%20worth%20up%20to%20Rs%203%2C350%20with%20vouchers%20from%20EaseMyTrip%2C%20Ajio%2C%20and%20Swiggy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Freliance-jio-announces-diwali-dhamaka-offers-swiggy-ajio-and-easemytrip-vouchers-with-these-plans%2Farticleshow%2F114581384.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Southern%20India%20Has%20A%20Problem%20Similar%20To%20Japan%2C%20China%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F0171fqhg_tamil-nadu-school_625x300_25_October_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20light-hearted%20comment%20made%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20over%20couples%20and%20children%2C%20soon%20after%20his%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20counterpart%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20advised%20people%20to%20have%20more%20offspring%2C%20has%20revived%20the%20debate%20over%20delimitation%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20southern%20states%2C%20which%20have%20lower%20population%20indices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2021%2C%20at%20an%20event%20organised%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Hindu%20Religious%20and%20Charitable%20Endowments%20department%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Stalin%20cited%20an%20old%20tradition%20of%20blessing%20people%20with%20wishes%20for%2016%20children%2C%20while%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20south's%20lower%20fertility%20rates%20could%20translate%20to%20weakened%20political%20power%20after%20delimitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20earlier%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20had%20declared%20his%20apprehensions%20about%20the%20ageing%20population%20in%20south%20Indian%20states.%20He%20said%20his%20government%20was%20contemplating%20incentivising%20families%20for%20having%20more%20children%2C%20keeping%20the%20future%20in%20mind.%20He%20also%20exhorted%20people%20of%20south%20Indian%20states%20to%20have%20more%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Naidu%20and%20Stalin%20spoke%20in%20different%20contexts%2C%20their%20remarks%20highlight%20the%20common%20concern%20of%20southern%20states%20over%20the%20disadvantages%20of%20a%20dwindling%20as%20well%20as%20ageing%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESouth's%20elderly%20population%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20reflects%20the%20ageing%20population%20and%20falling%20fertility%20rates%20in%20India%20-%20by%202050%2C%20one%20in%20every%20five%20persons%20will%20be%20above%2060.%20For%20southern%20states%2C%20it%20is%20still%20grimmer.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20southern%20states%20have%20seen%20a%20noteworthy%20demographic%20shift%20as%20their%20total%20fertility%20rate%20(TFR)%20has%20fallen%20below%20the%20replacement%20level.%20The%20fertility%20rate%20in%20southern%20states%20at%201.6%20was%20below%20the%20national%20average%20of%20little%20above%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TFR%20is%20the%20average%20number%20of%20children%20that%20a%20woman%20will%20have%20during%20her%20reproductive%20years.%20A%20TFR%20of%202.1%20is%20considered%20the%20replacement%20level%20-%20a%20population%20can%20maintain%20its%20size%20across%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20India%20Ageing%20Report%202023%20compiled%20by%20the%20UNFPA%20(United%20Nations%20Population%20Fund%20and%20IIPS%20(International%20Institute%20for%20Population%20Sciences)%2C%20the%20proportion%20of%20elderly%20in%20the%20population%20will%20increase%20by%206%20to%207%25%20in%20the%20south%20compared%20to%203%20to%204%25%20in%20north%20India%20between%202021%20and%202036.%20Life%20expectancy%20is%20also%20high%20in%20the%20south.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouthern%20states%20shifted%20to%20a%20lower%20fertility%20rate%20much%20earlier%20than%20the%20northern%20states.%20According%20to%20statistics%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20is%20set%20to%20achieve%20the%20replacement%20level%20of%20fertility%20in%202025%2C%20more%20than%2020%20years%20after%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Having%20made%20the%20demographic%20transition%20before%20the%20north%20(particularly%20the%20states%20dubbed%20'BIMARU')%2C%20there%20are%20fears%20that%20southern%20states%20will%20pay%20the%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20south%20Indian%20states%20have%20successfully%20implemented%20family%20planning%20schemes.%20From%20birth%20control%20measures%20to%20educating%20women%2C%20South%20Indian%20states%20have%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20in%20population%20stabilisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaidu%20rightly%20cited%20countries%20with%20an%20ageing%20population%20-%20Japan%2C%20China%2C%20and%20European%20countries%20-%20facing%20a%20strain%20on%20their%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20reduced%20working-age%20population%20means%20less%20people%20contributing%20to%20the%20economy%20through%20work%2C%20taxes%2C%20and%20social%20security.%20In%20comparison%2C%20the%20proportion%20of%20elderly%20people%20who%20require%20pensions%20and%20healthcare%20security%20rises%2C%20putting%20a%20financial%20strain%20on%20both%20families%20and%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNorthern%20states%20are%20doing%20nothing%20to%20control%20their%20population.%20This%20naturally%20makes%20the%20southern%20states%20feel%20that%20they%20are%20being%20punished%20for%20implementing%20family%20planning%20measures%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Professor%20RV%20Ramana%20Murthy%2C%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20University%20of%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20divergence%20continues%2C%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20decades%2C%20the%20position%20of%20the%20southern%20states%20will%20be%20far%20worse.%20That%20is%20what%20the%20chief%20ministers%20(Naidu%20and%20Stalin)%20are%20trying%20to%20convey%2C%26quot%3B%20Murthy%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelimitation%20-%20a%20disadvantage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20of%20the%20Centre's%20plan%20to%20rearrange%20constituencies%20based%20on%20population%20has%20raised%20worries%20in%20southern%20states%20over%20the%20possible%20consequences.%20Any%20such%20realignment%20of%20constituencies%20would%20hand%20a%20political%20advantage%20to%20north%20Indian%20states%2C%20which%20have%20larger%20populations%2C%20as%20they%20would%20get%20more%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20compared%20to%20the%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20lurking%20fear%20that%20the%20delimitation%20process%2C%20scheduled%20to%20occur%20after%20the%20new%20census%2C%20would%20potentially%20diminish%20the%20influence%20of%20southern%20states%20in%20national%20decision-making%20as%20they%20would%20have%20fewer%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaidu%20and%20Stalin's%20remarks%20will%20also%20find%20support%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Kerala%2C%20which%20have%20already%20been%20calling%20out%20the%20bias%20of%20population%20numbers%20shaping%20devolution%20of%20central%20funds%20both%20in%20Parliament%20and%20outside%3B%20southern%20states%20are%20effectively%20being%20%26quot%3Bpenalises%26quot%3B%20for%20meeting%20population%20goals%2C%20they%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dispute%20over%20devolution%20of%20central%20funds%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20core%20subjects%20of%20frustration%20for%20southern%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20been%20constantly%20complaining%20that%20the%20devolution%20given%20to%20states%20has%20been%20significantly%20lower%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20compared%20to%20the%20recommended%20levels%20of%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission.%20Also%2C%20the%20share%20of%20devolution%20for%20the%20less%20populous%20and%20fiscally%20stronger%20southern%20states%20tend%20to%20be%20lower%2C%20while%20northern%20states%20that%20are%20weaker%20on%20these%20metrics%20get%20a%20larger%20share%20of%20central%20taxes%2C%20imply%20by%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20despite%20their%20substantial%20contribution%20to%20the%20GDP%20(over%2030%25)%20and%20population%20(19.6%25)%2C%20the%20southern%20states%20have%20seen%20their%20share%20in%20tax%20devolution%20decrease%20from%2021%25%20under%20the%2011th%20Finance%20Commission%20to%20just%2015.8%25%20under%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20applying%202011%20population%20criterion%2C%20southern%20states%20have%20lost%20their%20revenue%20share%20in%20the%20central%20pool.%20Further%2C%20southern%20states%20have%20an%20aging%20population%2C%20which%20increases%20the%20burden%20of%20provision%20of%20pension%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Murthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20needs%20to%20settle%20the%20misgivings%20and%20doubts%20about%20the%20delimitation%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20and%20assuage%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20south%20Indian%20states.%20They%20cannot%20be%20punished%20for%20achieving%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729849200000%2C%22visual%22%3A