me%20out%20on%20top.%20In%20Marathwada%2C%20all%20three%20parties%20from%20the%20MVA%20played%20their%20part.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20from%20the%20Mahayuti%2C%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20was%20ahead%20in%20the%20Thane-Konkan%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20dominated%20Northern%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20the%20two%20factions%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20only%20parties%20with%20a%20pan-state%20presence%20in%20the%20state%20and%20they%20led%20in%20assembly%20segments%20in%20all%20zones%20in%20the%20general%20elections.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20not%20in%20the%20lead%20in%20any%20assembly%20segment%20in%20the%20Thane-Konkan%20region%2C%20as%20was%20the%20case%20with%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20segment.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20failed%20to%20make%20a%20mark%20in%20Vidarbha%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Marathwada%20and%20North%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Shiv%20Sena%20factions%20are%20comparatively%20stronger%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20and%20Thane-Konkan%20regions%2C%20while%20NCP%20factions%20dominate%20Western%20and%20North%20Maharashtra.%20In%20Vidarbha%20and%20Mumbai%2C%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20the%20key%20players.%20And%20while%20the%20former%20leads%20in%20the%20North%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Uddhav-led%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20does%20so%20in%20the%20Marathwada%20regions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstanding%20The%20Six%20Regions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20demographics%20as%20well%2C%20these%20regions%20are%20very%20different.%20Marathwada%2C%20Vidarbha%20and%20Western%20Maharashtra%20have%20high%20SC%20populations%2C%20while%20ST%20groups%20are%20high%20in%20numbers%20in%20North%2C%20Vidarbha%20and%20in%20Thane-Konkan.%20Marathwada%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Thane-Konkan%20and%20North%20have%20a%20high%20Muslim%20population%20too.%20In%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20MVA%20did%20well%20in%20areas%20with%20high%20SC%20and%20Muslim%20populations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EVidarbha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eincludes%20Nagpur%2C%20Amravati%2C%20Akola%2C%20Gondiya%2C%20Bhandara%2C%20Yavtamal%2C%20Washim%2C%20Chandrapur%2C%20Gadhchiroli%2C%20Wardha%20and%20Buldhana%20districts.%20Notably%2C%20it%20houses%20the%20headquarters%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarathwada%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eincludes%20the%C2%A0Aurangabad%20division%2C%20the%20tourism%20capital%20of%20the%20state.%20A%20third%20of%20the%20state's%20Maratha%20population%20resides%20here%2C%20across%20Aurangabad%2C%20Osmanabad%2C%20Parbhani%2C%20Hingoli%2C%20Nanded%2C%20Beed%2C%20Latur%20and%20Jalna%20districts.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWestern%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%C2%A0popularly%20known%20as%20the%20sugar%20bowl%20of%20the%20state%2C%20includes%20the%20Pune%2C%20Satara%2C%20Sangli%2C%20Solapur%20and%20Kolhapur%20districts.%20The%20sugar%20belt%20of%20Western%20Maharashtra%2C%20unlike%20Vidarbha%20and%20Marathwada%2C%20is%20agriculturally%20rich.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ENorth%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0is%20home%20to%20the%20Nashik%20division%20and%20includes%20the%20Nashik%2C%20Dhule%2C%20Jalgaon%20and%20Nundurbar%20districts.%20It%20borders%20the%20state%20of%20Gujarat%20to%20its%20north.%20While%20Nashik%20is%20economically%20developed%2C%20other%20districts%20are%20comparatively%20backward.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThane-Konkan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20lying%C2%A0on%20the%20western%20coast%20of%20the%20state%2C%C2%A0%20is%20the%20third%20most%20industrialised%20zone%20in%20Maharashtra.%20It%20included%20the%20Thane%2C%20Palghar%2C%20Raigad%2C%20Sindhudurg%20and%20Kalyan%20districts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Mumbai%C2%A0region%20has%2036%20seats%20between%20Mumbai%20City%20and%20Mumbai%20suburban%20districts.%20A%20100%25%20urban%20region%2C%20it%20is%20the%20financial%20capital%20of%20the%20country%2C%20housing%20stock%20exchanges%2C%20headquarters%20of%20the%20biggest%20banks%2C%20and%20BFSI%20companies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgricultural%20and%20rural%20distress%20and%20farmer%20suicides%20are%20burning%20issues%20in%20Vidarbha%2C%20Marathwada%20and%20North%20Maharashtra.%20The%20BJP%20hopes%20that%20its%20Ladli%20Bahin%20Yojana%20will%20help%20neutralise%20the%20discontent%20with%20the%20government%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20in%20the%20highly%20industrialised%2C%20developed%20regions%20of%20Thane%2C%20Mumbai%20and%20Western%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20that%20its%20focus%20on%20infrastructure%20and%20progress%20will%20help%20it%20win.%20The%20Ladli%20Bahin%20Yojana%20may%20have%20less%20resonance%20here%2C%20but%20then%2C%20the%20Mumbai-Thane%20regions%20also%20house%20world's%20biggest%20urban%20slums%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20its%20impact%20cannot%20be%20entirely%20ruled%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Maratha%20Stir%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Maratha%20agitation%20has%20its%20roots%20in%20Marathwada%2C%20which%20has%2046%20seats.%20In%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20movement's%20leader%2C%20M.M.%20Jarange%20Patil%2C%20had%20called%20upon%20the%20people%20here%20to%20vote%20against%20the%20BJP-led%20government.%20He%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20field%20candidates%20from%20the%20Maratha%20community%2C%20hoping%20to%20become%20a%20kingmaker.%20This%20could%20divide%20the%20opposition%20vote%20and%20damage%20the%20MVA's%20prospects%2C%20at%20least%20in%20Marathwada.%20Amidst%20this%2C%20the%20BJP%20hopes%20to%20benefit%20from%20a%20counter-consolidation%20of%20OBCs%20who%20oppose%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Marathas%20in%20the%20OBC%20list.%20The%20state's%20ST%20bloc%20is%20also%20reeling%20under%20internal%20divisions%20as%20the%20Dhangar%20community%2C%20a%20traditional%20supporter%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20has%20been%20demanding%20inclusion%20in%20the%20ST%20list.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavigating%20these%20social%20equations%20and%20compulsions%20will%20be%20a%20big%20challenge%20for%20all%20the%20competing%20political%20parties%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20goal%2C%20though%2C%20is%20one%3A%20winning%20four%20out%20of%20Maharashtra's%20six%20zones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729845720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fmjn6peio_maharashtra_625x300_25_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaharashtra-elections-why-mva-and-mahayuti-must-focus-on-4-zones-6870181%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20is%20still%20grappling%20with%20seat%20finalisation%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20released%20its%20first%20list%20of%2099%20candidates.%20With%20elections%20due%20in%20a%20month%2C%20election%20fever%20has%20gripped%20the%20entire%20Maharashtra.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaharashtra-elections-why-mva-and-mahayuti-must-focus-on-4-zones-6870181%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20rags%20to%20riches%3A%20Dean%20Forbes%20crowned%20UK%E2%80%99s%20most%20influential%20Black%20person%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729845686000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-1