o%20just%20about%20one%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20margin%20of%20Aaditya%20Thackeray's%20win%20in%20the%202019%20state%20election%20-%20he%20had%20a%2065%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%20advantage%20-%20underlines%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20task%20for%20the%20Shinde%20Sena%20and%20Milind%20Deora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20will%20provide%20a%20boost%20is%20that%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20Worli%20voters%20gave%20Mr%20Sawant%20a%20very%20narrow%20win%20-%20he%20finished%20less%20than%207%2C000%20votes%20ahead%20of%20the%20Shinde%20Sena's%20Yamini%20Jadhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Third%20Challenger%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%20Thackeray%20could%20be%20the%20dark%20horse%20in%20this%20election.%20His%20MNS%20opted%20not%20to%20field%20a%20candidate%20from%20Worli%20in%202019%20to%20respect%20Aaditya%20Thackeray's%20electoral%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffor-aaditya-thackeray-a-challenge-likely-from-uncle-raj-thackerays-party-in-worli-seat-6259027%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFor%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%2C%20Worli%20Challenge%20Likely%20From%20Uncle's%20Party%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20all%20bets%20are%20off%20now%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20reduced%20margin%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20signals%20an%20opportunity%20to%20gain%20ground.%20%26quot%3BIn%202017%20(in%20municipal%20polls)%2C%20we%20bagged%20around%2030%2C000%20to%2033%2C000%20votes%20from%20Worli.%20We%20have%20voters%20dedicated%20to%20MNS%20here...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Deshpande%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAaditya%20Thackeray%2C%20though%2C%20is%20unfazed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BThe%20People%20Know...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20junior%20Thackeray%20led%20a%20massive%20rally%20Thursday%20as%20he%20filed%20his%20papers%2C%20and%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20the%