liated%20was%20indeed%20very%20shocking.%20It%20was%20appalling%20to%20see%20that%20such%20a%20senior%20Dalit%20leader%20was%20treated%20by%20the%20Congress%20Party%20with%20such%20utter%20disdain%20and%20disrespect%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20CR%20Kesavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELashing%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20practices%20untouchability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20shown%20what%20is%20Dalit's%20position%20in%20Congress.%20Outside%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20shows%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20supports%20Dalits%20and%20gives%20them%20equal%20participation.%20But%20inside%2C%20Dalits%20are%20insulted.%20What%20happened%20with%20Mallilarjun%20Kharge%20yesterday%2C%20after%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20left%20to%20tell%20people.%20Congress%20is%20exposed...Within%20the%20party%2C%20Dalits%20are%20insulted%20and%20treated%20as%20third-class%20citizens%2C%20and%20untouchability%20is%20practised...%26quot%3B%20said%20Chief%20Minister%20Sarma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20filed%20her%20nomination%20papers%20at%20the%20district%20collector's%20office%20at%20Kalpetta%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20her%20nomination%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20held%20a%20massive%20roadshow%20in%20Kalpetta%20town%20in%20Kerala%20and%20addressed%20a%20public%20rally%20where%20she%20expressed%20her%20gratitude%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad%20for%20supporting%20her%20brother%20in%20his%20difficult%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Wayanad%20seat%20was%20vacated%20by%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20(LoP)%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20who%20retained%20the%20Rae%20Bareli%20Lok%20Sabha%20Constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20by-poll%20in%20the%20Wayanad%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20on%20November%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729840440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2