3Cp%3EIn%20his%20post%2C%20the%20tech%20mogul%20said%20that%20his%20MRI%20indicated%20that%20his%20posture%20was%20trapping%20blood%20in%20his%20brain%2C%20blocking%20it%20from%20flowing%20properly%20to%20his%20heart.%20He%20further%20outlined%20the%20potentially%20life-threatening%20consequences%20of%20his%20condition.%20%26quot%3BWas%20I%20going%20to%20have%20a%20seizure%3F%20A%20stroke%3F%20I%20didn't%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20noting%20that%20many%20people%20may%20unknowingly%20face%20similar%20risks%20due%20to%20poor%20posture%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMy%20team%20and%20I%20went%20on%20Red%20Alert.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWe%20discovered%20through%20an%20MRI%20that%20my%20posture%20was%20trapping%20blood%20in%20my%20brain%2C%20blocking%20it%20from%20flowing%20properly%20to%20my%20heart.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWas%20I%20going%20to%20have%20a%20seizure%3F%20A%20stroke%3F%20I%20didn't%20know.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOcApHd2yeg%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FOcApHd2yeg%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Bryan%20Johnson%20%2Fdd%20(%40bryan_johnson)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbryan_johnson%2Fstatus%2F1844454196537590258%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20posture%20norms%20are%20pretty%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Johnson%20remarked%2C%20citing%20common%20practices%20such%20as%20slumping%20in%20a%20chair%20all%20day%20and%20looking%20down%20at%20screens.%20%26quot%3BPoor%20posture%20is%20normalized%20and%20it%20has%20all%20kinds%20of%20negative%20health%20effects%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20He%20also%20explained%20that%20such%20habits%20can%20lead%20to%20several%20health%20issues%2C%20including%20musculoskeletal%20pain%2C%20circulatory%20issues%2C%20digestive%20problems%2C%20impaired%20lung%20function%2C%20nerve%20compression%2C%20spinal%20misalignment%2C%20increased%20stress%2C%20fatigue%2C%20mood%20changes%2C%20lower%20motivation%2C%20and%20sleep%20disturbances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Johnson%20then%20revealed%20that%20five%20key%20habits%20that%20he%20claimed%20have%20dramatically%20improved%20his%20posture.%20First%2C%20he%20demonstrated%20a%20simple%20mental%20exercise%20that%20can%20remind%20you%20to%20maintain%20an%20upright%20posture.%20Second%2C%20he%20warned%20against%20looking%20down%20at%20devices%20and%20urged%20everyone%20to%20hold%20the%20phone%20at%20eye%20level%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20avoid%20bending%20the%20head%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20Mr%20Johnson%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20moving%20every%2030%20minutes%20throughout%20the%20day.%20%26quot%3BTake%20a%20brisk%20walk%3B%20climb%20some%20stairs%3B%20do%20some%20stretches%3B%20break%20out%20into%20dance.%20Anything%20active.%20Improved%20blood%20flow%20and%20a%20nice%20reset%20for%20posture%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20next%20tweet%2C%20he%20revealed%20two%20exercises%20to%20strengthen%20posture%20muscles.%20And%20in%20the%20next%20post%2C%20he%20acknowledged%20that%20strengthening%20neglected%20muscles%20can%20lead%20to%20initial%20soreness%2C%20but%20also%20reassured%20that%20this%20discomfort%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20progress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftech-millionaire-bryan-johnson-reveals-how-he-reversed-his-hair-loss-shares-tactics-6860617%5C%22%3ETech%20Millionaire%20Bryan%20Johnson%20Reveals%20How%20He%20Reversed%20His%20Hair%20Loss%2C%20Shares%20Tactics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImproving%20my%20posture%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20things%20I've%20done%20in%20my%20wellness%20efforts%20at%20Blueprint.%20Posture%20carries%20a%20profound%20psychological%20weight.%20When%20you%20stand%20tall%2C%20you%20exude%20confidence%20and%20self-acceptance%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Johnson%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImproving%20your%20posture%20doesn't%20just%20benefit%20you%3B%20it%20creates%20a%20ripple%20effect%20that%20encourages%20those%20around%20you%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20their%20own%20posture%20as%20well.%20In%20my%20family%2C%20whenever%20someone%20spots%20another%20person%20slouching%2C%20we%20make%20a%20%26quot%3Bzzzzzip%26quot%3B%20sound.%20Instantly%2C%20the%20person%20straightens%20up%2C%20often%20without%20even%20needing%20to%20say%20a%20word%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Mr%20Johnson%2C%20a%20former%20Silicon%20Valley%20executive%2C%20is%20known%20for%20his%20obsession%20with%20anti-ageing.%20He%20spends%20%242%20million%20a%20year%20on%20medical%20diagnostics%20and%20treatments%20combined%20with%20a%20meticulously%20crafted%20regimen%20of%20eating%2C%20sleeping%2C%20and%20exercising%20to%20see%20if%20he%20can%20slow%2C%20and%20perhaps%20even%20reverse%2C%20the%20ageing%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0A%20few%20days%20back%2C%20he%20revealed%20how%20he%20reversed%20male%20pattern%20baldness%20and%20restored%20his%20hair's%20natural%20colour%20in%20under%20a%20year.%20Before%20this%2C%20he%20claimed%20that%20he%20underwent%20a%20%26quot%3Btotal%20plasma%26quot%3B%20exchange%2C%20a%20radical%20procedure%20aimed%20at%20purging%20toxins%20from%20his%20body.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729837560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fvq8keb18_bryan-johnson_625x300_25_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftech-millionaire-bryan-johnson-shares-how-he-improved-posture-after-mri-scan-showed-it-was-killing-his-brain-6869480%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bryan%20Johnson%2C%20a%2046-year-old%20software%20millionaire%20who%20is%20on%20a%20quest%20to%20reverse%20his%20biological%20age%2C%20recently%20shared%20his%20astonishing%20transformation%20on%20social%20media%2C