oundation%2C%20an%20aftercare%20facility%20that%20empowers%20young%20adults%20who%20have%20aged%20out%20of%C2%A0%20childcare%20institutions%20(CCIs).%20It%20offers%20them%20more%20than%20just%20shelter%20%E2%80%94%20it%20gives%20them%20dignity%2C%20purpose%2C%20and%20a%20path%20to%20self-reliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemember%20the%20first%20time%20you%20stepped%20out%20of%20your%20home%2C%20unsure%20of%20which%20college%20course%20to%20pick%2C%20struggling%20to%20find%20that%20first%20job%2C%20or%20save%20enough%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20space%20in%20a%20new%20city%3F%20Adulting%20is%20tough%20%E2%80%94%20filled%20with%20confusion%2C%20complexity%2C%20and%20countless%20moments%20of%20self-discovery.%20Now%2C%20imagine%20navigating%20this%20transition%20without%20a%20family%20or%20support%20system%2C%20often%20with%20the%20added%20burden%20of%20emotional%2C%20physical%2C%20or%20even%20sexual%20trauma.%20This%20is%20the%20reality%20for%20thousands%20of%20youth%20who%20are%20forced%20to%20leave%20childcare%20institutions%20once%20they%20turn%2018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitting%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20two%20bustling%20cities%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20Chennai%2C%20the%20WeLive%20Foundation%20is%20reshaping%20how%20we%20think%20about%20young%20adults%20ageing%20out%20of%20government%20care.%20Over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20WeLive%20has%20empowered%20over%20175%20young%20people%20through%20its%20aftercare%20facility%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20by%20providing%20them%20with%20shelter%20but%20by%20equipping%20them%20with%20the%20skills%20and%20emotional%20resilience%20they%20need%20to%20find%20their%20footing%20in%20a%20world%20that%20can%20be%20unforgiving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20society%20that%20often%20overlooks%20these%20vulnerable%20young%20adults%2C%20WeLive%20has%20been%20making%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfiguring%20out%E2%80%9D%20phase%20of%20life%20a%20little%20easier%20for%20those%20who%20need%20it%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20lives%2C%20one%20step%20at%20a%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20WeLive%20began%20when%20one%20of%20its%20founders%2C%20a%20former%20CCI%20warden%2C%20saw%20firsthand%20the%20difficulties%20young%20adults%20faced%20upon%20leaving%20institutional%20care.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20few%20of%20them%20turned%2018%2C%20he%20took%20them%20into%20his%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Ramya%20Sundararajan%2C%20CEO%20of%20WeLive%20Foundation.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20experience%20sparked%20the%20idea%20for%20WeLive.%E2%80%9D%20The%20foundation%20opened%20its%20first%20centre%20for%20young%20men%20in%20Bengaluru%20in%20December%202020%2C%20with%20just%20five%20residents.%20Today%2C%20it%20has%20expanded%20to%20three%20residential%20programmes%20across%20Bengaluru%20and%20Chennai%2C%20supporting%20both%20men%20and%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_040_11zon-1729768067.jpg%3Ffit%3D1233%252C822%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221233%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22WeLive's%20residency%20programme%20focuses%20on%20well-being%20and%20work%20readiness%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_040_11zon-1729768067.jpg%3Fw%3D1233%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201233w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_040_11zon-1729768067.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_040_11zon-1729768067.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C333%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_040_11zon-1729768067.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C512%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%