to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363045%2Fgrassroots-organisations-initiatives-changemakers-teach-education-underprivileged-children-slum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20education%20more%20interesting%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20would%20allow%20them%20to%20experience%20what%20they%20were%20reading%20and%20learn%20by%20seeing%20real-life%20projects%20in%20action.%20The%20activities%20had%20to%20be%20engaging%2C%20fun%2C%20and%20never%20boring%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jitender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20quest%20led%20the%20administration%20to%20launch%20the%20%E2%80%98Schools%20on%20Wheels%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20aimed%20at%20keeping%20underprivileged%20children%20in%20school.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20day%2C%20the%20buses%20take%20these%20children%20to%20learn%20topics%20like%20aquaculture%2C%20seasonal%20farming%2C%20pond%20rejuvenation%20projects%2C%20etc.%20We%20wanted%20to%20inculcate%20the%20habit%20of%20reading%20and%20interaction%2C%20while%20bringing%20education%20closer%20to%20them%20%E2%80%94%20giving%20them%20that%20extra%20push%20to%20attend%20school.%20This%20approach%20allows%20them%20to%20learn%20in%20a%20stress-free%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-10-1729256143.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C628%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20buses%20are%20equipped%20with%20interactive%20learning%20materials%2C%20books%2C%20and%20educational%20videos.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-10-1729256143.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%