20would%20also%20give%20us%20new%2C%20colourful%20books%2C%20uniforms%2C%20and%20a%20variety%20of%20food.%20The%20teachers%20even%20taught%20us%20inside%20the%20school%20bus%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Preeti.%20Now%20a%20Class%204%20student%2C%20she%20has%20been%20regularly%20attending%20school%20for%20the%20past%20year%20and%20a%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20initiative%20was%20the%20first%20of%20many%20projects%20launched%20by%20Jitendra%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F344227%2Fnayi-disha-ngo-seema-seth-educates-underprivileged-kids-in-gurugram-senior-citizen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimprove%20the%20lives%20of%20underprivileged%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20women%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECombating%20anaemia%20and%20improving%20nutritional%20awareness%20in%20schools%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20in%20April%202022%2C%20the%202014%20batch%20IAS%20officer%20has%20been%20making%20significant%20strides%20in%20the%20district%20of%20Sangrur.%20Other%20than%20the%20Schools%20on%20Wheels%20programme%2C%20he%20has%20been%20implementing%20innovative%20projects%20to%20address%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20community%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311913%2Fassam-teacher-uttam-teron-educates-underprivileged-rural-children-for-free-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducation%20and%20health.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHealth%20and%20education%20are%20the%20basic%20foundations%20for%20a%20society.%20When%20the%20foundation%20is%20strong%2C%20the%20structure%20will%20definitely%20be%20strengthened.%20Women%20and%20children%20comprise%2065%20percent%20of%20our%20society%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20empowering%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-9_11zon-1729256204.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C628%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20administration%20also%20established%20kitchen%20gardens%20in%20public%20and%20private%20schools%20to%20promote%20the%20consumption%20of%20iron-rich%20foods.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-9_11zon-1729256204.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-9_11zon-1729256204.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-9_11zon-1729256204.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-9_11zon-1729256204.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C402%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-9_11zon-1729256204.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20data-recalc-dims%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371231%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20administration%20also%20established%20kitchen%20gardens%20in%20public%20and%20private%20schools%20to%20promote%20the%20consumption%20of%20iron-rich%20foods.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20year%2C%20IAS%20Jitendra%20conducted%20a%20survey%20in%20government%20schools%20and%20discovered%20that%20approximately%2048%20percent%20of%20students%20across%2021%20schools%20were%20anaemic.%20This%20was%20concerning%2C%20especially%20given%20that%20the%20Indian%20Government%20had%20been%20distributing%20Iron%20and%20Folic%20Acid%20(IFA)%20tablets%20through%20its%20Weekly%20Iron%20and%20Folic%20Acid%20Supplementation%20(WIFS)%20programme%20to%20combat%20the%20prevalence%20and%20severity%20of%20anaemia%20among%20adolescents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20tablets%20were%20being%20distributed%20every%20Wednesday%2C%20Jitendra%20observed%20that%20many%20children%20were%20hesitant%20to%20consume%20them%20due%20to%20misconceptions%20and%20lack%20of%20awareness.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20that%20there%20were%20incidences%20when%20children%20took%20IFA%20tablets%20and%20they%20fainted.%20Of%20course%2C%20their%20parents%20got%20worried%20and%20were%20suspicious%20of%20the%20free%20tablets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20speaking%20to%20a%20few%20health%20providers%2C%20I%20learnt%20that%20these%20tablets%20should%20not%20be%20taken%20on%20an%20empty%20stomach.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20underprivileged%20households%2C%20breakfast%20is%20not%20a%20common%20practice%2C%20so%20most%20children%20rely%20on%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20provided%20at%20school.%20However%2C%20they%20were%20given%20Iron%20and%20Folic%20acid%20tablets%20during%20morning%20prayers%2C%20which%20put%20them%20at%20risk%20of%20fainting%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20food%20beforehand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20he%20introduced%20changes%20to%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20programme%2C%20adding%20iron-rich%20foods%20and%20folic%20acid%20tablets%20to%20the%20diet%2C%20and%20educating%20parents%20and%20students%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20taking%20IFA%20tablets%20after%20meals%20to%20avoid%20adverse%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20smooth%20implementation%2C%20teams%20were%20formed%20at%20block%20and%20district%20levels%20to%20monitor%20the%20distribution%20and%20consumption%20of%20these%20tablets%2C%20with%20regular%20reports%20sent%20to%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%E2%80%99s%20office%20every%2015%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20also%20established%20kitchen%20gardens%20in%20nearly%20756%20public%20and%20private%20schools%20to%20promote%20the%20consumption%20of%20iron-rich%20foods%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20spinach%2C%20fenugreek%2C%20carrots%2C%20and%20drumsticks.%20The%20project%20saw%20a%20significant%20decrease%20in%20anaemia%20cases%20after%20a%20second%20health%20survey%20was%20conducted%20six%20months%20later%20in%20January%202024.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20anaemia%20percentage%20was%20brought%20to%20four%20percent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20women%20through%20entrepreneurship%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20education%20and%20health%20initiatives%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20also%20initiated%20projects%20to%20promote%20entrepreneurship%20and%20livelihood%20opportunities%20for%20women%20in%20local%20households%20under%20the%20PEHEL%20(Promoting%20Employment%20of%20Households%20through%20Entrepreneurship%20and%20Livelihood)%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20this%20project%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F255139%2Fmumbai-designer-covid19-underprivileged-women-earn-money-donation-livelihood-fashion-cloth-bags-scrunchies-gurmeen-shrivastav-srujna-ngo-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20underprivileged%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20self-help%20groups%20(SHGs)%20were%20engaged%20in%20the%20production%20of%20school%20uniforms.%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20the%20school%20committees%20allot%20the%20work%20to%20contractors%20but%20we%20roped%20in%20SHGs%20under%20the%20Punjab%20State%20Rural%20Livelihood%20Mission%20(PSRLM)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp