ents%20due%20to%20this%20reason.%20The%20brain%20just%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20function%20that%20way.%20Another%20problem%20I%20have%20is%20difficulty%20with%20attention%20to%20detail%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CADHD%20can%20often%20be%20identified%20in%20childhood%20or%20adolescence%2C%20and%20while%20it%20is%20manageable%2C%20getting%20diagnosed%20after%20entering%20the%20workforce%20can%20bring%20additional%20challenges.%20Adults%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD%20may%20experience%20heightened%20anger%2C%20stress%2C%20and%20relationship%20issues%2C%20alongside%20reduced%20dynamism%20and%20good%20spirit%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pompa%20Maitra%20Chakraborty%2C%20a%20clinical%20psychologist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIdentifying%20the%20challenges%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20his%20coping%20mechanism%2C%20Aalen%20acknowledged%20his%20reliance%20on%20caffeine%2C%20which%20provides%20him%20with%20comfort%2C%20even%20though%20it%20may%20not%20be%20the%20healthiest%20option.%20%E2%80%9CI%20drink%20a%20lot%20of%20coffee%20that%20helps%20me%20get%20through%20the%20day.%20There%20is%20a%20brief%20window%20after%20having%20caffeine%20where%20I%20can%20focus%20better%20and%20be%20productive.%20However%2C%20I%20have%20reached%20a%20point%20where%20my%20coffee%20consumption%20has%20increased%20significantly%2C%20leading%20me%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20sugar%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20reflecting%20on%20other%20times%20he%20resorted%20to%20unhealthy%20coping%20mechanisms%2C%20such%20as%20smoking%2C%20which%20ultimately%20lead%20to%20breathing%20difficulties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recounts%20his%20experiences%20in%20managing%20distractions%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%20discussing%20the%20strategies%20he%20employs%20to%20maintain%20focus%20amidst%20a%20busy%20environment.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20significant%20obstacle%20for%20me%2C%20as%20my%20work%20involves%20a%20lot%20of%20writing%20and%20requires%20me%20to%20be%20in%20front%20of%20a%20screen%20constantly.%20I%20find%20it%20hard%20to%20focus%20when%20there%20are%20people%20around%20or%20when%20there%E2%80%99s%20noise.%20While%20I%20struggle%20with%20concentration%20in%20general%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20distractions%20makes%20it%20even%20more%20challenging.%20To%20combat%20this%2C%20I%20use%20noise-cancelling%20headphones%20to%20minimise%20ambient%20noise.%20If%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20those%2C%20I%20always%20keep%20my%20earphones%20handy%2C%20which%20helps%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aalen%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20540px)%20100vw%2C%20540px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-17-at-23.36.00-1-1-1729686729.jpeg%3Ffit%3D500%252C645%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aalen%20Isaac%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-17-at-23.36.00-1-1-1729686729.jpeg%3Fw%3D540%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20540w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-17-at-23.36.00-1-1-1729686729.jpeg%3Fresize%3D232%252C300%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20232w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-17-at-23.36.00-1-1-1729686729.jpeg%3Fresize%3D500%252C645%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-17-at-23.36.00-1-1-1729686729.jpeg%3Fresize%3D150%252C194%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371952%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22697%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAalen%20suggests%20that%20regular%20exercise%20can%20improve%20focus%20and%20productivity%20for%20individuals%20with%20ADHD%20in%20the%20workplace%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ff